ath":"/6kvn74uKpZjomhEgmRbvCZXBWOV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/wFuUDqlO3pvkhBooVz9ZFnWCpbr.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dlyeSZD92Arha6XVBteyNNaPi19.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/noLtkNa2WkmWyKqxygmlXl4l38y.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.434},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/r54uZKIHuZENt56Xk4pKhPE91fV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:22:30.896+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Who Am I?","runtime":120,"tagline":"Fight now. Ask questions later.","homepage":"","overview":"A group of covert CIA operatives trailing a potential new energy source are double-crossed by corrupt agent Morgan, who causes a helicopter crash in remote South Africa. The sole survivor, suffering severe amnesia, is nursed to recovery by a kindly native tribe who call him \"Whoami\" after the question he keeps asking. With the help of a mysterious reporter Christine, Whoami pieces together his past and tracks the turncoat agent and his criminal cohorts."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Jackie Chan ist Nobody","runtime":120,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jackie ist Agent eines Eliteteams. Er soll mit seinen Kollegen eine Verbrecherbande in Afrika bestehlen, die in den Besitz eines Meteoriten gelangt ist. Mit dessen Hilfe kann man Waffen von unvorstellbarer Zerstörungskraft bauen. Jedoch stürzt Jackies Hubschrauber ab und alle außer ihm sterben. Er wird verletzt von Eingeborenen gefunden und gastfreundlich aufgenommen. Allerdings hat er sein Gedächtnis verloren. Als er später zu der Absturzstelle des Hubschraubers zurückkehrt, kann er sich dunkel erinnern und weiß, dass er in die Zivilisation zurück muss, um sein Gedächtnis zurückzuerlangen und die Vorkommnisse aufzuklären."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Senza nome e senza regole","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jackie Chan è un agente segreto che ha perso la memoria e non sa più chi è. Si perde in una tribù di africani, partecipa a una tappa della Parigi-Dakar e poi si trova a combattere usando zoccoli olandesi ad Amsterdam. Slapstick kung fu ad alto grado adrenalinico quello del regista/attore hongkonghese."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Qui suis-je ?","runtime":108,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un commando est envoyé en Afrique pour dérober une nouvelle arme très puissante. Dans l'avion, Jackie veut rattraper un traître mais il tombe de l'avion. Recueilli par des africains, il est devenu amnésique et les autochtones l'appelle \"Who Am I\", les seuls mots qui sortent de sa bouche. Mais lorsqu'il rejoint la vie urbaine, il cherche à tout prix retrouver son identité ainsi que le traître qui a tenté de le tuer et causé la mort de toute son équipe."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Az elveszett zsaru","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Furcsa férfira (Jackie Chan) bukkannak a bennszülöttek a sivatagban. A különös idegennek fogalma sincs, mi a csudát keres azon a vidéken, ahol életében nem járt, hogy hívják, és főleg: kik azok, akik a sivatagba is utána jönnek, hogy megöljék. Talán titkos ügynök volt? Néhány nyomból hamarosan összeáll a kép, Whoami (Jackie Chan) rájön, hogy kommandós volt, akit társaival együtt átvertek, és ő a csapat egyetlen túlélője. Most már csak arra kell valahogy visszaemlékeznie, hogy mindezért kin kell bosszút állni."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Кто я?","runtime":108,"tagline":"«Сражайся сейчас. Вопросы потом»","homepage":"","overview":"Группа спецназа, работающая под прикрытием ЦРУ, направляется на задание по вывозу энергетического тела, которое было найдено учеными в африканских джунглях. По окончании операции всю группу пытаются ликвидировать.  Один из солдат, выживший после авиакатастрофы, но потерявший память, пытается бороться со своими мыслями и вспомнить, кто он. На пути к истине ему мешают, и он не знает, кому можно верить."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"¿Quién soy?","runtime":0,"tagline":"Primero dispara. Pregunta después.","homepage":"","overview":"Jackie es reclutado por la CIA para formar parte de un comando de élite, que recibe la orden de asaltar un laboratorio secreto de armamento tecnológico en la jungla africana. Traicionados por su jefe, todo el equipo muere excepto Jackie, que es abandonado inconsciente en la jungla. Una tribu le recoge y le cura, aunque sufre de amnesia que le impide saber quién es y cómo llegó hasta allí. Su lucha por descubrir su verdadera identidad le hará sufrir la persecución de sus antiguos enemigos, y no podrá confiar en nadie nunca más. (FILMAFFINITY)"},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"De CIA heeft het plan opgevat om met een groepje speciaal getrainde commando's een basis diep in de binnenlanden van Afrika aan te vallen. Daar wordt door criminele topmannen in het diepste geheim gewerkt aan de ontwikkeling van nieuwe terroristische wapens. De aanval is een groot succes, toch keert het team niet terug van de missie. De CIA heeft geen enkel aanknopingspunt, de inheemse bevolking wel. Die hebben in de oerwouden een zwaar gewonde soldaat gevonden die ze inmiddels al maanden verplegen. Ze noemen de soldaat 'Who Am I', want dat is het enige wat hij uit kan brengen. Hij is zijn geheugen kwijt en moet op zoek om zijn identiteit te ontdekken. Hij is ook de enige die de waarheid achter de mislukte missie kan achterhalen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Identidade Perigosa","runtime":0,"tagline":"Luta agora. Faz perguntas depois.","homepage":"","overview":"Um agente secreto perde a memória depois de cair de um helicóptero que se despenhou. É então perseguido por vários outros agentes da agência, mas não faz ideia porquê."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"我是谁","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"三名科学家在非洲大陆发现了一种神秘的矿石，这种矿石具有极强的杀伤力。就在这三名科学家携带矿石返回的途中，美国中央情报局派出了由11名来自不同国家的特种兵组成的特别行动小队将科学家和他们成果劫持了。情报局内部出现了内鬼，想把这一成果据为己有。于是，他命令负责接应的飞行员制造了一次空难，以此来杀人灭口和掩饰其已夺取了成果。特别行动小队几乎全军覆灭，只有队员杰克（成龙 饰）侥幸逃生。当杰克被当地的土著救活时，他因剧烈的碰撞而丧失了所有记忆，自己的名字、来历通通都一无所知。他逢人只会问“我是谁”。为了查明自己的身世，杰克回到了纽约……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"フー・アム・アイ？","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ある秘密特殊部隊が任務の終了後、組織の裏切りにより、移動中の飛行機ごと始末される。重傷を負い、記憶を失いながらも原住民に助けられ、“フーアムアイ”の名で部落に迎えられた工作員の一人は、自らの記憶を取り戻すため部落を離れ一人旅立つ。しかし、彼の生存を知った組織は、口封じのため刺客を送りこむ。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Who Am I","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En gruppe kommandosoldater deltager i en hemmelig operation i den afrikanske jungle. Efterfølgende lader CIA deres fly styrte ned for at slette alle spor. Kun en enkelt agent (Jackie Chan) overlever, men han kan ikke huske, hvem han selv er. Desværre bliver han genkendt af en fyr fra CIA og må efterfølgende forsøge at undslippe diverse lejemordere, alt imens han forsøger at opklare gåden om sin egen identitet."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Mstitel beze jména","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Poté, co byl po brutálním zásahu CIA prohlášen za mrtvého, musí osamělý mstitel rychle najít svou pamět, aby odhalil mezinárodní špionážní spiknutí, které chce uvést do provozu nový smrtonosný zdroj energie. S pomocí dvou krásných bojovnic musí Jackie překonat kontinenty a čelit ozbrojeným zabijákům a zlověstným spiknutím na každém kroku."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"מי אני?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ג'קי צ'אן מחפש את זהותו בסרט אקשן על סוכן חשאי של ה-CIA שניצל מתאונת מסוק, אבל חוטף מכה בראש ושוכח הכל. הוא נוחת אצל בני שבט דרום אפריקאי, לומד את מנהגיהם ולאט לאט מנסה להרכיב מחדש את הפאזל של חייו. העניין נעשה מסוכן כשמנסים להתנקש בחייו והוא לא יודע למה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"성룡의 C.I.A","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"재키는 CIA 소속 특공대원. 그는 다른 특수 대원들과 함께 남아공의 최첨단 무기 연구소를 기습, 세명의 과학자를 납치하고 원폭과도 같은 위력을 지닌 무기로 개발 가능한 운석 에너지를 탈취하는데 성공한다. 그러나, 작전을 마무리 하고 귀환하던 중, 특공대 리더는 대원들을 사살하고 무기를 빼돌린다. 유일한 생존자인 재키는 그대로 정글에 버려지나 원주민들이 그를 구해낸다.  그러나, 그는 사고의 충격으로 기억을 잃은 상태. 원주민들로 부터 'Who Am I'란 이름을 얻고 그들과의 생활에 적응해 나가던 어느날, 재키는 우연히 랠리에 참가중인 자동차 행렬을 보게 되고 마침내 자신의 잃어버린 기억을 찾아 길을 떠나게 되는데. 재키는 도중에 사고를 당한 레이서 유키와 그녀의 오빠를 치료해 주다 랠리에 함께 참가하게 되고 무사히 목적지에 도착한 후 재키의 활약이 신문에 발표된다. 음모의 주역인 CIA의 간부 모건과 셔먼 장군은 재키의 생존 소식을 듣고 그를 없애려 한다.  한편, 홀로 위험에 빠진재키에게 미모의 사진기자 크리스틴이 접근, 그를 돕겠다고 나서는데. 차츰 자신의 기억을 되찾기 시작한 재키는 서서히 음모의 정체를 알게 되고 단서를 찾아 네덜란드로 향한다. CIA의 모건일당은 재키를 제거하려 혈안이 되고 크리스틴과 재키는 쉴 틈없이 닥쳐오는 위기를 겪으며 마침내 CIA 본부로 잠입하는데."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Zgadnij, kim Jestem?","runtime":0,"tagline":"Najpierw atakuj, potem zadawaj pytania.","homepage":"","overview":"Jackie Chan gra samotnego komandosa, którego szefowie z CIA posyłają na pewną śmierć. Teraz musi odzyskać pamięć i stawić czoła uzbrojonym zabójcom, którzy ścigać go będą po całym świecie. Musi przy tym nie tylko rozwikłać zagadkę swojej tożsamości, ale i powstrzymać grupę międzynarodowych szpiegów zmierzających do przejęcia kontroli nad najpotężniejszym źródłem energii na świecie."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Quem Sou Eu?","runtime":108,"tagline":"Lutar agora, as perguntas ficam pra depois...","homepage":"","overview":"Deixado para morrer por um agente traidor da CIA, um soldado (Chan) luta para recuperar a memória e desfazer um elo internacional de espionagem, antes que inimigos possam acionar uma poderosa e mortal fonte de energia. Com o auxílio de duas belas ajudantes, Jackie abre seu caminho através de continentes, enfrenta assassinos armados e planos sinistros em cada esquina. Para elevar os níveis de adrenalina e ação espetacular, não há nada melhor do que Jackie Chan."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Who Am I?","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En grupp kommandosoldater genomför en lyckad operation, men en av deras chefer är förrädare. Helikoptern som gruppen färdas i sprängs och bara en av soldaterna överlever. Han hittas av infödingar, oskadd men utan minne."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Cine sunt eu?","runtime":0,"tagline":"Luptă acum. Pune întrebări mai târziu.","homepage":"","overview":"Un grup de agenți ascunși ai Agenției de Inteligență Centrale (CIA) care urmăresc o potențială nouă sursă de energie sunt înșelați de agentul corupt Morgan, care provoacă o prăbușire de elicopter în îndepărtata Africa de Sud. Singurul supraviețuitor, care suferă de amnezie severă, este îngrijit pentru recuperare de un trib nativ amabil care îl numește „Cinesunteu” după întrebarea pe care o tot pune. Cu ajutorul unei reportere misterioase Christine, Cinesunteu își împletește trecutul și îl urmărește pe agentul de turnare și cohortele sale infracționale."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Afrika Kaplanı","runtime":0,"tagline":"Şimdi dövüş, sonra sor.","homepage":"","overview":"Chan, tüm meslektaşlarının öldüğü bir helikopter kazası tuzağından belleğini yitirmiş olarak çıkan bir ajandır. Olup biteni anlamakta güçlük çekmektedir. Uyandığında kendisini bile hatırlamamaktadır. Afrikada uyanan bu adama Afrikadakiler Adın ne? diye sorunda o da Kimim Ben? diye yanıt verince insanlar ona Kimim Ben demeye başlar. Afrikadan sonra Hollandaya gelen bu adam, bir süre sonra kendisinin büyük bir tuzak içinde olduğunu anlar. Ve şimdi bir sürü insanın ölümüne neden olan bir kaset için savaşacaktır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"من کیستم؟","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"افریقای جنوبی. پس از سقوط یک هلی کوپتر حامل گروهی از مأموران سیا، «جکی» (چان) زنده می‌ماند. اما کمی بعد می‌فهمد که دچار فراموشی شده و باید به گذشته‌ی خود پی ببرد. در بازگشت به ژوهانسبورگ، خبرنگاری به نام «کریستین» مقاله‌ای درباره‌ی «جکی» به چاپ می‌رساند و به این ترتیب مأموران فاسد سیا به تکاپو می افتند تا «جکی» را از بین ببرند..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"我是誰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"摩根及彼得連同十二名不同國藉的突擊隊員，其中包括積奇，伏擊一支貨車車隊，擄走三名科學家並搶走魔岩。  摩根及彼得在完成任務後，設下陷阱，令到全體突擊隊員喪生，但事與願違，積奇大難不死，並流落到一條偏僻的非洲村落。他身負重傷，而且失了記憶，對自己的身份和身處當地的經過毫無切象。積奇日漸康復，稍後偶然在森林深處發現直升機殘骸，突然記起一些往事。  開始有些頭緒。 積奇看見一架撞毀的賽車，救了被蛇咬的日本司機愛次，還把賽車修理好。雪感恩，順道送積奇到開普敦。  在開普敦，一個金髮美女姬絲汀向積奇自稱是記者，要為他的經歷作特寫報道。摩根現身向積奇查問，積奇告訴魔根其他突擊隊員已經死了。摩根致電彼得，要他殺掉積奇。 姬絲汀幫積奇解開爛報紙上的密碼。積奇知道他如果要知道自己的身份和遭人追殺的理由，便要到鹿特丹......"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Кой съм аз?","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Той не може да си спомни кой е, но спомни ли си - ще бъде мъртъв."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Men kimman?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ozbek","iso_639_1":"uz","iso_3166_1":"UZ","english_name":"Uzbek"},{"data":{"title":"¿Quién soy yo?","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jackie es reclutado por la CIA para formar parte de un comando de élite, que recibe la orden de asaltar un laboratorio secreto de armamento tecnológico en la jungla africana. Traicionados por su jefe, todo el equipo muere excepto Jackie, que es abandonado inconsciente en la jungla. Una tribu le recoge y le cura, aunque sufre de amnesia que le impide saber quién es y cómo llegó hasta allí. Su lucha por descubrir su verdadera identidad le hará sufrir la persecución de sus antiguos enemigos, y no podrá confiar en nadie nunca más."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Who Am I?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En hemmelig agent mister hukommelsen etter å ha falt fra et styrtende helikopter. Han jages så av flere andre agenter, men har ingen anelse om hvorfor."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"我是誰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"美國中央情報局在南非發現了一塊魔石，中情局南非局長為了獨佔魔石，在委派9名特殊隊員搶走魔石及捉拿3名科學家時，也藉機製造空難事件滅口。但被犧牲的隊員中卻有一個奇跡生還，就是中情局香港支局，代號523號的隊員-積奇。  積奇生還後出現失憶，忘掉自己的身份、過去和名字，流落在南非的土人族群中，土人族從他的服裝上的號碼和其零碎記憶中的「523號」取名為「我是誰」，之後在拉力賽中來到南非市區。我是誰﹝積奇﹞在市區的醫院裏認識了一位女記者，在她的協助下被安排到荷蘭的鹿特丹，但我是誰卻發現女記者的身分並不單純。我是誰為自救，決定自行查出真相，但另一方面，得知其生還消息的中情局南非局長和其手下為了滅口正等待積奇的到來..."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Pomstiteľ bez mena","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na juh Afriky vyšlú prísne tajné medzinárodné komando CIA, ktoré má uniesť vedecký tím pracujúci na meteorite, ktorý je neuveriteľne silným zdrojom energie. Celá akcia prebieha hladko, až kým sa úspešný tím nemá vrátiť na základňu. Vyjde najavo, že akcia nebola tak úplne legálna a všetky stopy majú byť zničené. Jediný, komu sa podarí prežiť haváriu vrtuľníka je agent Jackie, ktorého s ťažkým zranením objavia domorodci. Vylieči ho, no stratil pamäť. Nejaký čas žije s domorodcami, ale túžba objaviť tajomstvo stratenej minulosti je silnejšia a tak sa rozhodne pátrať po svojej totožnosti. Cestou zachráni automobilového pretekára uhryznutého hadom a pomôže jeho spolujazdkyni doraziť víťazne do cieľa. Týmto na seba upútal pozornosť. A tak sa Jackie čoskoro ocitá v ohrození a musí využiť všetky schopnosti. Pomáhajú mu pritom nielen zvedavá novinárka, ale aj sympatická pretekárka, ktorá sa s ním vydá do holandského Rotterdamu, kde by mohol nájsť odpovede na všetky svoje otázky."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"ใหญ่เต็มฟัด","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เฉิน หลง ร่วมปฎิบัติการคอมมานโดลับสุดยอด แต่ทั้งคณะกลับถูกตลบหลัง หวังฆ่ายกคณะบนเฮลิคอปเตอร์กลางป่าอัฟริกา เขารอดมาได้เพียงคนเดียวเพราะร่วงลงมาก่อนเครื่องระเบิด แต่ก็ความจำเสื่อม ไม่รู้ว่าตัวเองเป็นใคร มาจากไหน เขาได้อาศัยชาวเผ่าพื้นเมืองช่วยกันรักษาจนแข็งแรง และเริ่มศึกษาประเพณีวัฒนธรรมของชาวเผ่า เมื่อความทรงจำของเขาค่อยๆฟื้นคืนมา เฉิน หลง ก็ขอตัวกลับไปค้นหาตัวตนที่แท้จริง พร้อมความสามารถพิเศษเพิ่มเติมจากช่าวเผ่า ท้ายที่สุดแล้ว เฉิน หลง จะรู้ไหมว่า เขาคือใคร และจะปิดบัญชีแค้นได้สำเร็จหรือไม่"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Tko sam ja?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Skupinu tajnih CIA-inih operativaca koji prate potencijalni novi izvor energije dvostruko prelazi korumpirani agent Morgan koji uzrokuje pad helikoptera u udaljenoj Južnoj Africi. Jedinog preživjelog, koji pati od teške amnezije, njeguje ljubazno domaće pleme koje ga naziva \"Whoami\" nakon pitanja koje neprestano postavlja. Uz pomoć tajanstvene reporterke Christine, Whoami sastavlja svoju prošlost i prati agenta prelaznika i njegove kriminalne kohorte."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"ვინ ვარ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"სპეცნაზის ჯგუფი მიემართება დავალებაზე ენერგიული სხეულის გამოძახებაზე, რომელიც მეცნიერებმა იპოვეს აფრიკის ჯუნგლებში. ოპერაციის დასრულების შემდეგ ჯგუფის ლიკვიდაციას სცდილობენ. ერთერთი ჯარისკაცი, რომელიც ავიაკატასტროფის შემდეგ გადარჩა, მაგრამ მეხსიერება დაკარგა, სცდილობს მთელი არსებით ებრძოლოს მეხსიერებას და გაიხსენოს ვინ არის სინამდვილეში. სიმართლის გაგების გზაზე მას ხელს უშლიან და მან არ იცის ვის დაუჯეროს და ვის არა."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Хто я?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Група спецназу, що працює під прикриттям ЦРУ, виконує завдання з вивозу енергетичного тіла, що було знайдено вченими в африканських джунглях. По закінченні операції всю групу намагаються ліквідувати. Один із солдатів, що вижив після авіакатастрофи, але втратив пам’ять, намагається боротися зі своїми думками й згадати хто він. На шляху до істини йому заважають і він не знає кому можна вірити."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Jackie Chanin Taistele!","runtime":108,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jackie osallistuu huippusalaiseen kommandoiskuun. Tehtävänä on tuhota uusi superase, joka kykenee hävittämään kokonaisia kaupunkeja kerrallaan. Iskuryhmän helikopteri tuhoutuu. Vain Jackie pelastuu, mutta ei muista mitään - ei edes omaa nimeään. Eikä sitä ehdi jäädä miettimään, kun niskaan hengittää jatkuvasti laumoittain tappajia."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Tôi Là Ai","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Thành Long vào vai một điệp viên mật bị mất trí sau khi nhảy xuống khỏi một chiếc trực thăng. Không những thế, anh còn bị truy sát bởi một nhóm người mà anh không biết tại sao mình lại bị chúng truy đuổi... Bằng những kỹ năng tuyệt đỉnh của mình. Liệu anh có tìm lại được con người thật của mình và chiến thắng những kẻ truy sát?"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Kas aš esu?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Slaptasis agentas praranda atmintį iššokęs iš krentančio sraigtasparnio. Jį vaikosi kiti agentai, bet jis net nenutuokia, kodėl."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Jackie Chan perd la mémoire","runtime":120,"tagline":"Combattez maintenant. Posez les questions plus tard.","homepage":"","overview":"Un commando est envoyé en Afrique pour dérober une nouvelle arme très puissante. Dans l'avion, Jackie veut rattraper un traître mais il tombe de l'avion. Recueilli par des africains, il est devenu amnésique et les autochtones l'appelle \"Who Am I\", les seuls mots qui sortent de sa bouche. Mais lorsqu'il rejoint la vie urbaine, il cherche à tout prix retrouver son identité ainsi que le traître qui a tenté de le tuer et causé la mort de toute son équipe."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"5614d0c6c3a368681401c4ed","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5614d0c6c3a368681401c4ed","author":"DeepSpace","content":"The car chase scenes were awesome! The fight scenes are outstanding! This is probably my favorite Jackie Chan movie. I particularly like the chase scene in the city with the Lancer Evo IV. The whole desert scenario with the rally Montero is hilarious, too! It is capped off with one of Jackie Chan's best fight scenes ever in the end. A must see!","created_at":"2015-10-07T07:59:02.972Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:37.639Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"DeepSpace","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":10622,"adult":false,"title":"Mr. Nice Guy","video":false,"overview":"A Chinese chef accidentally gets involved with a news reporter who filmed a drug bust that went awry and is now being chased by gangs who are trying to get the video tape.","genre_ids":[80,28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.721,"vote_count":729,"poster_path":"/wAAt2gvbkbeefzjd06GPfkdfUho.jpg","release_date":"1997-01-31","vote_average":6.525,"backdrop_path":"/2RzrugSbC1iFI6fnsvUuk0wqzTc.jpg","original_title":"一個好人","original_language":"cn"},{"id":9056,"adult":false,"title":"Police Story","video":false,"overview":"Officer Chan Ka Kui manages to put a major Hong Kong drug dealer behind the bars practically alone, after a shooting and an impressive chase inside a slum. Now, he must protect the boss' secretary, Selina, who will testify against the gangster in court.","genre_ids":[28,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0166,"vote_count":1004,"poster_path":"/1eFB0Iy1TMU4VO5hMcoCE064JAT.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-14","vote_average":7.527,"backdrop_path":"/eYDAnSidN4rIEuneS5gEJkTyk3l.jpg","original_title":"警察故事","original_language":"cn"},{"id":33542,"adult":false,"title":"Rumble in the Bronx","video":false,"overview":"Keong comes from Hong Kong to visit New York for his uncle's wedding. His uncle runs a market in the Bronx and Keong offers to help out while Uncle is on his honeymoon. During his stay in the Bronx, Keong befriends a neighbor kid and beats up some neighborhood thugs who cause problems at the market. One of those petty thugs in the local gang stumbles into a criminal situation way over his head.","genre_ids":[80,28,35,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.465,"vote_count":1125,"poster_path":"/1nAfchiXHQB3iyhK8fCJJEnNs5A.jpg","release_date":"1995-01-21","vote_average":6.821,"backdrop_path":"/5ftRls3IbR1kXnasqJEJL63LVsc.jpg","original_title":"紅番區","original_language":"cn"},{"id":9404,"adult":false,"title":"Police Story 4: First Strike","video":false,"overview":"Hong Kong cop Chan Ka-Kui returns, working with Interpol to track down and arrest an illegal weapons dealer. Chan later realizes that things are not as simple as they appear and soon finds himself to be a pawn of an organization posing as Russian intelligence.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0025,"vote_count":518,"poster_path":"/bRHbteT4IORJOXY0Qrnb4FPXRS0.jpg","release_date":"1996-02-10","vote_average":6.477,"backdrop_path":"/gYLSKuxOOmUGu0fZvErHz2FkZGl.jpg","original_title":"警察故事4之簡單任務","original_language":"cn"},{"id":42218,"adult":false,"title":"Empire of the Ants","video":false,"overview":"A Florida real estate developer and her captain lure investors to a property in the Everglades called Dreamland Shores, under false pretenses that the swampland will soon be developed. After the group arrives on a small island, they find it has been overrun by giant mutated ants, brought on by the dumping of toxic waste in the area.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2202,"vote_count":126,"poster_path":"/6cmuKjH92h2wrBlbj0WPaTdnpnl.jpg","release_date":"1977-06-29","vote_average":4.9,"backdrop_path":"/fZqKC0Dw420APMovCTdneSURJDb.jpg","original_title":"Empire of the Ants","original_language":"en"},{"id":40508,"adult":false,"title":"3 Ninjas Knuckle Up","video":false,"overview":"Rocky, Colt and TumTum must battle an evil wealthy toxic waste dumper in order to save a local Indian tribe and their friend Joe. The 3 Ninjas must help find Joe's father and find a secret disk that contains evidence that could stop the toxic landfill that is destroying the Indian community. However the town is owned by the rich man and he controls the police and even the mayor. They must fight a motorcycle gang and renegade cowboys in this non-stop ninja adventure.","genre_ids":[10751,12,28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9882,"vote_count":207,"poster_path":"/A2664BFz1Xmxyprh9DoxXIEldhb.jpg","release_date":"1995-04-07","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/fU8X7GbEkUvhn6rSH58mR8VHcUO.jpg","original_title":"3 Ninjas Knuckle Up","original_language":"en"},{"id":2008,"adult":false,"title":"The Promise","video":false,"overview":"An orphaned girl, driven by poverty at such a young age, makes a promise with an enchantress. In return for beauty and the admiration of every man, she will never be with the man she loves. This spell cannot be broken unless the impossible happens: snow falling in spring and the dead coming back to life. Now a grown and beautiful princess, she regrets her promise, for all of the men she's loved has always been met with tragedy.","genre_ids":[14,18,28,53,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9386,"vote_count":131,"poster_path":"/tdm4mlc27S1d72ub4Y4xcU2OlDD.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-15","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/AwlJ2bQGjfEuXLsL5XJAaxOmMuV.jpg","original_title":"无极","original_language":"zh"},{"id":50435,"adult":false,"title":"Bilitis","video":false,"overview":"A coming of age story centering on the exploits of a young girl during summer vacation.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.0837,"vote_count":104,"poster_path":"/uhebKo7EuNJpSTfOorWxDCQQJAn.jpg","release_date":"1977-03-16","vote_average":5.24,"backdrop_path":"/hcIAUiFR3CZudxpBqZR6t47Eduz.jpg","original_title":"Bilitis","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1493425,"adult":false,"title":"Morgan: Killer Doll","video":false,"overview":"Things go awry when Astrid doesn't share the same feelings for her longtime best friend, Darcy.","genre_ids":[27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5395,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/eZaITue9TqLzxILtiunBoQ448Pd.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-13","vote_average":5.758,"backdrop_path":"/jfSjAU29orZXCDgX8uNInR2GRhK.jpg","original_title":"Morgan: Killer Doll","original_language":"en"},{"id":18758,"adult":false,"title":"To Kill with Intrigue","video":false,"overview":"Young master Cao Le chases his pregnant girlfriend away from the family castle. He does it in order to save her from vicious bandits who are going to murder his family.","genre_ids":[28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.676,"vote_count":54,"poster_path":"/n4tHrGkapp4LIN5kyj8IvjoYaUf.jpg","release_date":"1977-07-22","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/2TmcDKB95sprJ2HM7xRggRU92ty.jpg","original_title":"劍花煙雨江南","original_language":"zh"},{"id":13827,"adult":false,"title":"Surfer, Dude","video":false,"overview":"A wave twisting tale of a soul searching surfer experiencing an existential crisis.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.799,"vote_count":116,"poster_path":"/948AdP72iLQUjWvKp9r8981PT28.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-05","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/cZ4uvNu0fbMOjbXn1U24O56wqdN.jpg","original_title":"Surfer, Dude","original_language":"en"},{"id":27472,"adult":false,"title":"The Odd Couple II","video":false,"overview":"Brucey, the son of Oscar, calls his father to invite him to his wedding to Felix's daughter next Sunday in California. Oscar and Felix meet again at Los Angeles International Airport and rent a car in order to go to San Malina for the wedding.","genre_ids":[12,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9264,"vote_count":146,"poster_path":"/aTajf9LOrL1pok7KnzoHKFJJyWD.jpg","release_date":"1998-04-09","vote_average":6.332,"backdrop_path":"/hJQ8SRUp8DgNaqgszlwh9RUUXJB.jpg","original_title":"The Odd Couple II","original_language":"en"},{"id":16081,"adult":false,"title":"Doctor Dolittle","video":false,"overview":"A veterinarian who can communicate with animals travels abroad to search for a giant sea snail.","genre_ids":[10402,10751,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9037,"vote_count":194,"poster_path":"/rViuZo27U8wcZHGuRliv9LfmhjV.jpg","release_date":"1967-12-05","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/6zuQ0AbgMqPvyldXz82NKvYtYqU.jpg","original_title":"Doctor Dolittle","original_language":"en"},{"id":77248,"adult":false,"title":"Genius Party Beyond","video":false,"overview":"Five stories, five maestros, five styles and one common denominator: maximum creativity. Studio 4°C, the coolest label on the planet, invites us for the second time to an exclusive reunion of a talents with a group film, full of freedom and ingenuity, that goes from Mahiro Maeda's classic anime, to Kazuto Nakazawa's intricate urban sketches, Shinya Ohira's bedlam of color and Tatsuyuki Tanaka's animated cyberpunk. And as if that wasn't enough, Koji Morimoto, the studio big boss, is charge of putting the icing on the cake with fantafabulous piece of abstract poetry that would make a VJ die of ecstasy. The party of the year.","genre_ids":[16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6363,"vote_count":54,"poster_path":"/uGZbRSafiU6A2Ek5idLWS7yGR4U.jpg","release_date":"2008-10-11","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/tq2NLdey0CwfW2tmOjFwIkmBE0W.jpg","original_title":"ジーニアス・パーティ・ビヨンド","original_language":"ja"},{"id":31659,"adult":false,"title":"Wise Guys","video":false,"overview":"Harry Valentini and Moe Dickstein are both errand boys for the Mob. When they lose $250,000, they are set up to kill each other. But they run off to Atlantic City and comedy follows.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7081,"vote_count":116,"poster_path":"/oN4xnH6SqigBlyTlOnOkZ2tdWAB.jpg","release_date":"1986-04-17","vote_average":5.409,"backdrop_path":"/mBOl4RHVpIxIXaPapG6RIr3qH1Q.jpg","original_title":"Wise Guys","original_language":"en"},{"id":741318,"adult":false,"title":"Zero to Hero","video":false,"overview":"Biopic tribute to So Wa Wai, Hong Kong's first Paralympic athlete to win gold. Even if you start at a disadvantage, you can still be first across the finish line.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7653,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/zLO2uXFvic6tDQCvNFpZbJNCJGN.jpg","release_date":"2021-08-12","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/exQxYRTEfzj9Mmnk6Ku6hk52t2d.jpg","original_title":"媽媽的神奇小子","original_language":"cn"},{"id":15325,"adult":false,"title":"God Grew Tired of Us","video":false,"overview":"Filmmaker Christopher Quinn observes the ordeal of three Sudanese refugees -- Jon Bul Dau, Daniel Abul Pach and Panther Bior -- as they try to come to terms with the horrors they experienced in their homeland, while adjusting to their new lives in the Un